{"tid":129983,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"水邊圍邨爐火燒屋 街坊拖喉合力救","createTime":"2017-02-22T05:00:20.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-22T05:10:42.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"bf26114fc0055d96ed53c6495436d3313f815faf","tid":129983,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T05:00:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20170222/19936546\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20170222%2F19936546&d=R%2BBR62t8sBL7FL0rmd5Y1Z4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=7da8f2c1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20170222%2F19936546&h=729d5d98\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20170222/19936546</a><br />\n<br />\n水邊圍邨爐火燒屋<br />\n街坊拖喉合力救<br />\n<br />\n4,278<br />\nInitial ImagePlay Button Image<br />\n適中字型<br />\n較大字型<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】元朗水邊圍邨一單位女戶主昨午煮食期間，火舌燃著雜物發生火警，冒出大量濃煙，街坊曾自行拖喉救火不果，消防員接報到場將火救熄，女戶主一家三口與另外一男一女，分別吸入濃煙及腳傷須送院治理，起火單位付諸一炬。<br />\n<br />\n中午12時許，元朗水邊圍邨碧水樓4樓一單位，姓歐女戶主（60歲）在廚房煮食，疑火舌燃著旁邊雜物引起火警，歐婦與79歲姓黃丈夫與19歲兒子慌忙逃生。街坊鄭先生表示，他當時在2樓平台聽到巨響，赫見該單位冒出濃煙，附近有地盤工人立即拉喉，他亦協助救火，樓上走廊亦有街坊拉喉撲救，「總共4條喉，但水力唔係好夠，當時好大煙，但唔係好大火，盡量救啦！」消防員其後趕至現場，出動一喉一煙帽隊，23分鐘後將火救熄，其間疏散約30名居民到安全位置。<br />\n<br />\n火警中戶主一家三口，以及53歲姓司徒女保安員及姓馮煤氣公司男職員，分別吸入濃煙及腳傷需送院治理。消防員調查後相信火警無可疑，起火單位遭嚴重焚毀。  <br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n貓咪困工廈水渠　消防擔梯救<br />\n下一則<br />\n警破勝和武器庫　開山刀三國無雙咁款"},{"pid":"316a76c3d4021a5a2c46c70c2256b5c3f230107b","tid":129983,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T05:01:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/video/20170222/org/1487707439_a651.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fvideo%2F20170222%2Forg%2F1487707439_a651.jpg&h=1a7b9120&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e978a4cc7955b1fb71cef0d2451010bc4cf041e9","tid":129983,"uid":20943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T05:02:41.000Z","msg":"啲年紀咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n丈夫79歲<br />\n老婆就60<br />\n個仔19<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32e313fd45e92bb691fd783068f8e4038e52af2a","tid":129983,"uid":2923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T05:04:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>啲年紀咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n丈夫79歲<br />\n老婆就60<br />\n個仔19<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n老公60歲老母40歲生仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b919b9c1025b60e2a41e84045143b906e9d5968","tid":129983,"uid":8938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T05:06:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>啲年紀咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n丈夫79歲<br />\n老婆就60<br />\n個仔19<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n老公60歲老母40歲生仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n高齡產婦好易出事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"add5a5beaae8e3d50205912c470ef18cea5e4f38","tid":129983,"uid":17628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T05:10:42.000Z","msg":"地下射上四樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}